headline: Globe Life (GL) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of insurance holding company Globe Life (NYSE:GL) jumped 2.7% in the afternoon session after TD Cowen raised its price target on the stock to $199 from $182 and maintained a "Buy" rating.
